ref=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=cc753069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，教育家中兩老<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.16 @Template End@"},{"pid":"5f5c270b23b345a2dfde035eccf52a39a7d2c68f","tid":1572720,"uid":217874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:27:10.000Z","msg":"我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3705b69d5c9784e064c2589123331a4d5b645b4","tid":1572720,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d0f68ced43cb47f6eb820f97a6456b2b1b06804","tid":1572720,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"聽日狗記者會一定會話岳義士拎警棍攻擊狗隻<br />\n一定會話係恰當武力<br />\n記者可以反問返點解普通人都可以手持警棍<br />\n佢係咪休班狗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪自己人打自己人?因為手持警棍<br />\n點樣分佢真係警定係冒警<br />\n依加連紋身佬拎警棍都話自己係休班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點樣先知係真真正正既休班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請backup 警方涉嫌自編自導自演<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572558