學隻狗話齋 休班狗持警棍方便佢地可以係休息時執法 令到社會更加安全<br />\n反問佢地係咪想警員冇得休息 <br />\n剝削警員休息時間 係咪當警員係一件工具<br />\n再衍生到社會安全 但令到自己前線警員一啲都唔安全 好似依件事咁 係咪想罔顧自己警員生命安全<br />\n而達到你地同政府打壓市民出街嘅自由？<br />\n用一個扮關心狗隻嘅問題去問佢地<br />\n之後可以問返我post既問題<br />\n死都要咬住班黑警唔放 唔可以比佢地咁安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋岳義士仲有福建幫要煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e411e6a51d3aaa36d5712f044ec37543244e348a","tid":1572720,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845de37ed0f77ac01dd59bbfa2b8855ae76c2bfd","tid":1572720,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ee59c7190c86903fd1950a5e38e687b7d8a832","tid":1572720,"uid":18223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1cc67748d523b09b62c1ba174cf6eb2a096c153","tid":1572720,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bf5a9c42664f483c052e1761b1e4f625669fd0","tid":1572720,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220ef2203713b89280b4c1e95fbfc9571f5366de","tid":1572720,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}